title: PERSONAL SHOPPER Official Trailer (2017) Kristen Stewart Movie HD
author: ONE Media
comment: I thought this movie was gonna be about getting great deals while shopping and exposing the phony side of salesmen . I was wrong.

I honestly thought this was going to be Chick-flick. Like Cash-strap Kristen becomes a personal shopper for a rich Trophy-wife in New York, and there is a love interest somewhere in there. Or she becomes the Personal shopper for a rich handsome single guy who can't take care of him self and Romance ensue. Boy i was Wrong
No matter what people say, I absolutely love her ❤❤❤
A captivating performance of Kristen Stewart playing Kristen Stewart.
Wait i am so confused. What is this movie about? A Personal Shopper? A murder mystery? Or some paranormal shit? I would be making that same confused face that Kristen is making.
